race.comment: Siding with the Autumn Stakes form won by Observer which was a strongly run 1400m and should hold up well. CROCODILE (7) finished seventh there after settling on the rail having won well fresh. He's by Ghaiyyath and should improve going to 1800m. He maps beautifully and double figures in early betting looks generous, MASTER OF THE AIR (6) got back there but worked home fairly for eighth. He's one who will relish the trip and does draw to sit closer now. ARCORA (1) was just behind him in ninth. He ran second in the Derby before a spell and is another suited up in trip. He could look to be positive now. SINGLE CHOICE (4) ran well fresh over this trip and should strip fitter. MISS MARANDA (15) is flying, this is a fair bit tougher though.
